{"id":"12313","name":"Shazam Link Converter","tagline":"Shazam Link Converter is a shortcut to convert Shazam links to any other platform via Odesli.","icon":"ios15 c3679049983 g59756","latest":"34639","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><img alt=\"Shazam Link Converter\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xfHcrvg/Shazam-Link-Converter-Badge.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>Shazam Link Converter</strong> is a shortcut to convert Shazam links to any other platform via Odesli.</p>\n<h1>How to use it</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Choose a song in Shazam</li>\n<li>Click the Share button</li>\n<li>Select this shortcut from the actions list</li>\n<li>IMPORTANT: If the shortcut is stuck, just exit the Shazam app (swiping bottom up). If after choosing from the menu option it is stuck again, swipe bottom-up once more.</li>\n<li>The shortcut will find the corresponding iTunes and the Odesli link (https://odesli.co) for you if it exists.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Alternative way, if you already got the Shazam link:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Copy the Shazam link in the Clipboard</li>\n<li>Open this shortcut</li>\n<li>The shortcut will get the link from the Clipboard</li>\n<li>The shortcut will find the corresponding iTunes and the Odesli link (https://odesli.co) for you if it exists.  </li>\n</ol>\n<h1>What you get</h1>\n<p>If you pass a <strong>Shazam</strong> link, for example:  </p>\n<p>● <a href=\"https://www.shazam.com/track/202529158/19-minuets-k-103-no-1-in-c?referrer=share\">https://www.shazam.com/track/202529158/19-minuets-k-103-no-1-in-c?referrer=share</a></p>\n<p>You will get back an iTunes/Apple Music URL like this one:  </p>\n<p>● <a href=\"https://geo.music.apple.com/it/album/_/1599812537?i=1599836875&amp;mt=1&amp;app=music&amp;ls=1&amp;at=1000lHKX&amp;ct=odesli_http&amp;itscg=30200&amp;itsct=odsl_m\">https://geo.music.apple.com/it/album/_/1599812537?i=1599836875&amp;mt=1&amp;app=music&amp;ls=1&amp;at=1000lHKX&amp;ct=odesli_http&amp;itscg=30200&amp;itsct=odsl_m</a>  </p>\n<p>You will also get the <strong>Odesli</strong> link to a web page with many corresponding links (Amazon, Amazon Audio, Boomplay, Anghami, iTunes, Apple Music, Youtube, etc) like this one:  </p>\n<p>● <a href=\"https://song.link/i/1452175527\">https://song.link/i/1452175527</a>  </p>\n<p>You will also get the option to <strong>copy the link to the Clipboard</strong>, to just <strong>display it</strong> or to <strong>directly open it</strong>.  </p>\n<p><strong>NOTE:</strong> This shortcut is NOT an audio grabber. If you need that functionality, you can look at my other shortcuts: <a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/12242/\"><strong>SONGS Hunter</strong></a> and <a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/12578/\"><strong>MUSIC Grabber</strong></a>.  </p>\n<h1>IMAGES</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"Shazam Link Converter\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/M9tcbxg/Rainbow-From-The-Original-Motion-Picture-Soundtrack-My-Little-Pony-The-Movie-by-Sia.png\">  </p>\n<h1>USAGE AS EXTERNAL HELPER</h1>\n<p>You can call <em>Shazam Link Converter</em> from your own shortcut.<br>\nYou just need to pass a Dictionary with a single entry.<br>\nThe key must be '<strong>shazamurl</strong>' and the value must be the shazam link.<br>\nThe shortcut will return the corresponding <strong>youtube</strong> link, if it exists.<br>\nIn the future I will add the option to specify the type of url you want to get back.<br>\nYou can take a look at my other shortcuts <a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/12242/\"><strong>SONGS Hunter</strong></a> and <a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/12578/\"><strong>MUSIC grabber</strong></a> to see how it works.  </p>\n<h1>REQUIREMENTS</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>You need the Shazam app installed.  </li>\n</ul>\n<h1>ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS</h1>\n<p>This shortcut was inspired by <a href=\"https://routinehub.co/shortcut/9367/\">YouTube Music</a>  (author: <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/u/FelikZ\">FelikZ</a>). Thanks! :D </p>\n<h1>INFO</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>First Release:  2022-06-14  v1.0.0  </li>\n<li>Latest Release:  2022-08-17  v1.1.1  </li>\n<li>